data.name: label9.Text
data.value: This is an application that will assist you when performing your daily tasks as an electrician, to ensure acuracy and no errors please check that your input has no foreign characters in such as letters before pressing the calculate function. To use this program simply input your desired resister values and press the calculate button, the answer will then be provided next to the button (BOTH BOX'S MUST BE FILLED IN ORDER TO OPERATE)
